# Home Intelligence Agent вҖ” Revised Architecture Plan

---

## Project Overview

A FastAPI + LangGraph ReAct agent that answers questions about your home using your
actual documents as its knowledge base. The agent autonomously decides which tools
to call вҖ” RAG search over your documents, web search, or image analysis. It maintains
conversation memory within a session and outputs structured actions that n8n executes
(calendar events, tasks, notifications).

---

## Architecture Summary

