---

## Build Phases

### Phase 1 вҖ” Project Setup вң… DONE
Repo, venv, dependencies, config, logger, errors, FastAPI running.

### Phase 2 вҖ” Document Ingestion вң… DONE
Loader, chunker, Pinecone vectorstore, POST /api/ingest working.

### Phase 3a вҖ” Linear Agent вң… DONE
Basic linear graph (retrieve вҶ’ classify вҶ’ reason вҶ’ assess_urgency вҶ’ respond).
Proved the pattern works. Will be replaced by ReAct version.

### Phase 3b вҖ” ReAct Agent Conversion
- Remove ALL linear nodes (classify, assess_urgency, respond, retrieve)
- Update state schema with messages, image, actions, thread_id fields
- Create search_home_docs tool (RAG вҖ” wraps existing vectorstore.retrieve_similar)
- Create web_search tool
- Create image_analysis tool
- Build reasoning node with all tools bound to LLM
- Build execute_tools node
- Build ReAct graph with conditional loop
- Handle max iterations, tool errors, token budget
- Inject available actions into agent system prompt
- Agent outputs structured actions in state

### Phase 3c вҖ” Session Memory
- Add MemorySaver checkpointer to graph.compile()
- Pass thread_id from API request through to agent invocation
- Agent remembers previous messages within the same thread
- Update /api/ask to accept optional thread_id
- Streamlit maintains a thread_id per session
- Memory is in-process only (resets on server restart вҖ” not persistent)
- Persistent memory (PostgresSaver) pinned as future work

### Phase 4 вҖ” Action Queue
- Create SQLite-based action queue
- Create dispatcher (stores actions after agent finishes)
- Create GET /api/actions/pending endpoint
- Create POST /api/actions/complete endpoint
- Update ask route to dispatch actions after agent returns

### Phase 5 вҖ” Logging & LangSmith вң… DONE
Python logging in all nodes. LangSmith tracing verified.

### Phase 6 вҖ” Evals
- Gold standard Q&A dataset
- Eval runner using LangSmith
- Test answer relevance, tool selection accuracy, action correctness
- Evals gate prod deploys in GitHub Actions

### Phase 7 вҖ” Tests
- Unit tests for tools, action queue, agent nodes
- Integration tests for API endpoints
- Mock LLM calls for deterministic testing

### Phase 8 вҖ” GitHub & CI/CD
- Branch strategy (dev вҶ’ main)
- GitHub Actions: test on dev, test + eval on main
- Deploy hooks to Render

### Phase 9 вҖ” Render Deployment
- Dev and prod Render services
- Environment variables configured
- Deploy hooks wired to GitHub Actions

### Phase 10 вҖ” Streamlit UI
- Chat interface (not single Q&A вҖ” maintains thread_id per session)
- Image upload for "what is this?" questions
- Document upload for ingestion
- View action history (pending/completed)
- Deploy to Streamlit Cloud pointing at prod API

### Phase 11 вҖ” n8n Workflows
- Polling workflow: GET /api/actions/pending every 30s
- Switch node routing by action type
- Google Calendar integration
- Task list integration (Sheets or Notion)
- Notification integration (Slack or email)
- POST /api/actions/complete after execution
- Auto-ingest workflow: Google Drive watch вҶ’ POST /api/ingest

